      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg type="letterhead"><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00020"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb29424" type="org">Deut<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>che Zeitung</rs></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb198" type="place">IX., Pelikanga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e 4</rs>.</hi></seg><salute rend="center">Lieber Freund!</salute></opener><p>Von Ihrer Anfrage über <rs ref="#pmb11740" type="person">Loris</rs> hat man mir
               nichts mitgeteilt. Ich ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>e morgen entweder zwi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen
                  <time>3</time> u. <time>4</time><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00241-1"/><rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb168765"><rs ref="#pmb168765" type="place">Burgring</rs></rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00241-1"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs>
                  dürfte nach dem Tod seines <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12695" subtype="implied">Vaters</rs> dessen <rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb168765">Ordination</rs> weiter betreut haben.</note> oder um <time>½ 5</time><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb412" type="place">Grillparzer<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tr</rs>. Daß Sie <hi rend="underline" n="1">uns</hi> u. nur uns keine Notiz über <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00241-2"/><rs ref="#pmb213" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Ischler</hi></rs> Aufführung<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00241-2"><rs type="event" ref="#pmb35284" subtype="implied">Uraufführung</rs> von <rs ref="#pmb30005" type="work">Abschiedssouper</rs>, <ref target="1893-07-14" subtype="date-only" type="schnitzler-tagebuch"/>.
               </note> ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chickt, i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t nicht<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chön.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/>Ihr<lb/><signed>HermannBahr</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
